title: History of the Jelly Bean | Illuminating Moments in American
description:
See more: http://TheBlaze.com/TV.

A look at the jelly bean's American snacking history - from its origin, to the Great Depression and beyond. This is an "illuminating moment in American history" (as first seen on TheBlaze TV show "Liberty Treehouse").
